#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the <button>Download invoices</button> button</h2>
<button>Download invoices</button> will download the expense reports as PDF files
generated for this driver.  Note that these invoices are regenerated from database
data, which will probably be but not necessarily be the same thing as was sent to
the distributor management to be reimbursed.

